note=jart/cosmopolitan ljson tool/net/ljson.c JSON string decoder accepted overlong UTF-8 before kJsonStr table. Fix baf51a4 parent ccd057a. Witness c080 (overlong U+0000). Implemented as G42 (#66). Relation corrected from round_trip to value_oracle: the buggy decoder copies bytes verbatim so round_trip is identity and misses it; the acceptance gap needs value_oracle.
